  st_transform(4326) # safety of unprojected CRS

pearpopup <- paste0("<b>TYPE: ", pear$Common_Nam, "</b><br />Height: ", pear$HEIGHT_FT)

leaflet(pear) %>%
                addTiles() %>%
                 addSymbolsSize(values = as.numeric(pear$HEIGHT_FT),
                 lat = ~Latitude, 
                 lng = ~Longitude,
                 shape = 'triangle',
                 color = 'green',
                 fillColor = 'green',
                 opacity = .5,
                 popup=pearpopup,
                 baseSize = 5)
